options.text: Tell me how to balance kegs.
May I claim my tokens please?

e57d9756-7958-4524-81c1-1d0e73a994cd.title: <player>
e57d9756-7958-4524-81c1-1d0e73a994cd.text: May I claim my tokens please?

6efbe832-8d22-4f6f-8e56-bb61488193c9.title: Jimmy
6efbe832-8d22-4f6f-8e56-bb61488193c9.text: Wha'? You ain't earnt any mate!

a3b59833-3f95-4e94-a557-1657edc7e45f.title: <player>
a3b59833-3f95-4e94-a557-1657edc7e45f.text: Tell me how to balance kegs?

5a617f70-44df-4532-ab93-df047310646f.title: Jimmy
5a617f70-44df-4532-ab93-df047310646f.text:
Yer very very shtrange. But.... you pick the keg up,
and balance it on yer head, then you pick another keg
up and put that on top. S'really very eashy.

d8d23ff4-3c68-4c66-9614-a93bd45d36dd.title: Jimmy
d8d23ff4-3c68-4c66-9614-a93bd45d36dd.text: But you couldn't ever balansh ash many ash meee!

d3c52eb1-143d-4a32-92fa-e0884fc1b091.title: <player>
d3c52eb1-143d-4a32-92fa-e0884fc1b091.text: That sounds like a challenge, I'll show you!

f7265f92-aa74-44ca-9323-bff4a5dc743a.title: Jimmy
f7265f92-aa74-44ca-9323-bff4a5dc743a.text: Thish here'sh a shtore room right?

15003c4c-e98a-46e2-9ef4-bccb4c8c9c40.title: Jimmy
15003c4c-e98a-46e2-9ef4-bccb4c8c9c40.text:
That'sh what I shaid! *HIC* A shtore room.... Now
technic'ly shpeaking, I should be outshide guarding it...

e2e2a753-62c6-488d-973f-bb1c439c3df2.title: <player>
e2e2a753-62c6-488d-973f-bb1c439c3df2.text: But you just nipped in to have a quick drink?

0b9f4e71-06c3-40f6-a551-6dfb7f152ef3.title: Jimmy
0b9f4e71-06c3-40f6-a551-6dfb7f152ef3.text: Shure you wouldn't like an ickle drinkie fore yer go?

c5500395-8064-431c-822b-92dc5cee9c81.title: <player>
c5500395-8064-431c-822b-92dc5cee9c81.text:
No thanks, got things to do, people to see, tokens to
earn...
